div.p:
—Rota: operating base for nine [less than 1 line not
                        declassified] submarines and a support base for Navy [less than 1 line not declassified] logistics [less
                        than 1 line not declassified] in the Mediterranean;

1. We should seek to retain as many of the present and desired military rights
                    and facilities as are possible within the limits of a sustainable quid pro quo;
                    negotiations to this end should not be protracted.
